data.text:
Sweden U19 live scores, players, season schedule and today’s results are available on Sofascore.

Sweden U19 next match

We may have video highlights with goals and news for some Sweden U19 matches, but only if they play their match in one of the most popular football leagues.

Sweden U19 previous match

Sweden U19 previous match was against Italy U19 in U19 European Championship Qualif., the match ended in a draw (2 - 2).

Sweden U19 fixtures tab is showing the last 100 football matches with statistics and win/draw/lose icons.

There are also all Sweden U19 scheduled matches that they are going to play in the future.

Sweden U19 performance and form graph is a Sofascore unique algorithm that we are generating from the team's last 10 matches, statistics, detailed analysis and our own knowledge.

This graph may help predict future Sweden U19 matches.

Current Sweden U19 players

Forward: Alieu Njie, Emmanuel Tannor, Leonardo de Oliveira, Gottfrid Rapp Midfielder: Pontus Dahbo, Kazper Karlsson, Adrian Skogmar, Ture Sandberg, Gideon Granström, Adam Stroud Defender: Elison Makolli, André Álvarez Pérez, Anes Cardaklija, Charlie Axede Goalkeeper: Elis Bishesari

The current Sweden U19 roster, stats and player performance can be found on this page.

There are also statistics for each player in all competitions with all total played and started matches, minutes played, number of goals scored, number of cards and much more.

Sweden U19 top scorers list is updated live during every match.

You can click on players from the roster above and see available personal information such as nationality, date of birth, height, preferred foot, position, player value, transfer history etc.
